# Authenticated-tier UI master

For the **authenticated app** (everything except `public/`, `landing/`, and marketing/auth pages like `AuthPage`, `Offer*`, `Trial*`, `Subscription*`, `Terms*`, `Invite*`, `PWAAuthPage`), build UI from the master. Reference: `frontend/MASTER_STYLE_GUIDE.md`.

## Always use the master, never raw equivalents

- **Surfaces:** `.app-card` / `.app-card-interactive|elevated|flat|muted` or `<AppCard>` — NOT raw `bg-white rounded-xl border shadow-*`.
- **Buttons:** `.app-btn` + `.app-btn-primary|secondary|ghost|danger` or `<Button>` — NOT raw `<button className="px-.. py.. bg-..">`.
- **Inputs:** `.app-input` + `.app-label` + `.app-help` — NOT raw `border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-*`.
- **Modals/pop-ups:** `ModalFrame` with the **`size`** prop (`sm|md|lg|xl|2xl|full`) + `ModalHeader`/`ModalBody`(`rail` for forms)/`ModalFooter`/`ModalFieldGrid`. No glass (`bg-white/70 backdrop-blur`) panels; solid white + `shadow-app-modal`.
- **Loaders/empties/alerts:** `<SectionLoader>`/`<PageLoader>`/`<Skeleton>`, `<EmptyState>`, `<InlineAlert>` — NOT ad-hoc `animate-spin` or hand-rolled banners.
- **Headers:** `<PageHeader>` / `<SectionHeader>`. **Toasts:** `notify` from `src/lib/notify` (one `<AppToaster>` only).

## Color = tokens only

Use `primary` (brand green), `evidence` (teal = info), `impact` (success/active/done), `gray`, plus `amber/red` for warn/danger. **Never** `blue-/green-/emerald-/sky-/indigo-` (off-palette). `evidence` has shades 50–700 only.

## Convert-on-touch

When you edit a file that still hand-rolls a card/button/input with raw utilities, convert it to the master class/primitive in passing (keep diffs minimal otherwise). This grows master coverage instead of letting it drift.

## Imports

Relative paths only (no `@/` alias in Vite): `import { Button, PageHeader } from '../components/ui'`, `import ModalFrame, { ModalHeader } from '../ModalFrame'`.
